item.title: Year in Review 2020
item.description: 2020 ends with the pandemic. WFH is the new normal. Many thanks to my company, I was staying at home for most of last year. Family My daughter was born last year. Here name is Yoyo. Thanks for the WFH, that I could stay with her most of the time.
